@vrothberg referring to the comment by @holgerpieta I am also having the same problem with the proposed solution on `CentOS 8.4.2105`. This causes systemd to mark the job as failed with the result `protocol`...

Edit:
I have had some progress by configuring my unit file to enable cgroup delegation via `Delegate=yes`. However, as I don't see that in #10557 I am curious if the same problem will exist when using rootless containers with a `User` directive.

@holgerpieta did you ever resolve this? 

I am having the exact same issue. Is there a solution? 

`user@1001.service: Got notification message from PID 632662, but reception only permitted for main PID 1530`
